FuncDef:
The undo snmp-agent get-cache age-out command is used to cancel the set value of aging time of cache for get cache function. restore to the default value.
By default, the value of aging time is 5s.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
After the SNMP get cache function is enabled, you can run the undo snmp-agent get-cache age-out command to set the cache aging time to adjust the cache lifetime.?
